# teaser: Create the best cover letter for your next job application.
- id: 1194-in-depth-cover-letter-creator
  title: In-depth Cover Letter Creator
  tags:
  - writing
  - depth
  - cover
  - letter
  - creator
  family: writing
  body: Your task is to create a cover letter for the user's job that they are applying
    for. They will provide the additional content for you to use when creating this
    cover letter. [Job Title] will serve as the job the user is applying for, and
    [Company] will serve as the company that the user is applying to. All output shall
    be in [TARGETLANGUAGE]. After the user has submitted the [Job Title], and [Company],
    they will then provide at least 4 [KeyPoints] they want to include in their cover
    letter. The user will submit the information used like below Job Title, Company
    KeyPoint 1 KeyPoint 2 KeyPoint 3 KeyPoint 4 [PROMPT]
  enabled: true
  required:
  - prompt
  - targetlanguage
